hopobject.body: Will I get travelling expenses? what is vgr 100 It may be recalled, in this connection, that following Singh and US President Barack Obama reaffirmed last month their desire to further strengthen defence trade cooperation, endorsing a Joint Declaration on Defence Cooperation, Indian media carried reports to the effect that India-Russia defence relationship was losing its “closesness and warmth,” with New Delhi’s tilt towards Washington.
